        "TileImage": "$($repository 6a6d2edb-7048-482d-9c3e-02fb46dce0a1).Image",
        "Description": "Another team of assassins have found you 47, it's going to be a busy evening! This group are all posing as security guards:\n\nThe Guardian is watching the rooftops above the club;\nThe Tail is guarding the rear entrance to the club;\nThe Sentry is hanging around the Juice Bar;\nThe Bear is ensuring that the forest area remains clear.\n\nTake them out before they can reach you 47, and good luck.\n\nThis contract was made by Crewdy for the HITMAN Community Roadmap. Join our discord at https://hitman.community/discord for more information!",
